Name

qt_dictionary_iterator_create - allocate a concurrent dictionary iterator

Synopsis

#include <qthread/dictionary.h>

qt_dictionary_iterator *
qt_dictionary_iterator_create (qt_dictionary *dict);

Description

This function creates a dictionary iterator. The iterator points to the first element of the dictionary dict.

Return Values

Returns an initialized qt_dictionary_iterator object, or NULL if something went wrong.

See Also
